<div class="container container-m">
    <h2>Howdy, I'm Mike</h2>

    <p>I make some <a href="/projects">fun stuff</a>, write <a href="/blog">blog posts</a>, and co-founded and run <a href="https://www.presto-assistant.com">Presto Assistant</a>. I used to teach band and drums. Some of my students called me "Sensei". So <code>drumsensei</code> kinda stuck. I'm usually betwixt code and music.</p>

    <p>I'm lurking on Mastodon as <a href="https://social.lol/@drumsensei">drumsensei@social.lol</a>. Learn more <a href="/about">about me</a> or <a href="/about/colophon">about this site</a>.</p>

    <div class="titlebox">
      <h2 class="titlebox__name">Posts</h2>

      {%- for post in collections.homePagePosts %}
          <div class="post-list-item">
              <div class="post-list-item--data">
                <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
                <hr>
                <span class="post-list-item--date">{{ post.data.date.toISOString() | isoDateOnly }}</span>
              </div>
          </div>
      {% endfor %}
      <a class="titlebox__link" href="/blog">All Posts &rarr;</a>
    </div>

    <div class="titlebox">
      <h2 class="titlebox__name">Links</h2>

      {%- for post in collections.links.slice(0, 5) %}
          <div class="post-list-item">
            <div class="post-list-item--data">
              <a href="{{ post.data.link }}">{{ post.data.title }} <span style="font-weight: normal;">&nearrow;</span></a>
              <hr>
              <span class="post-list-item--date">
                <a href="{{ post.data.permalink | stripIndex }}">{{ post.data.date.toISOString() | isoDateOnly }}</a>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
      {% endfor %}
      <a class="titlebox__link" href="/links">All Links &rarr;</a>
    </div>


    <div class="titlebox">
        <h2 class="titlebox__name">Projects</h2>
        <div class="home-projects" style="margin-top: 25px;">
            {%- for project in site.projects.featured %}
              <div class="home-project">
                <img alt="{{ project.title }} logo" class="home-project--image" src="/assets/projects/{{ project.image }}">
                  <a href="{{ project.link }}">{{ project.title }}</a>
              </div>
            {% endfor%}
        </div>
        <a class="titlebox__link" href="/projects">All Projects &rarr;</a>
    </div>
</div>
